text:
The #NHS is sending text messages to some people to invite them to book a #COVID19 #vaccine appointment.
The message will be sent from ‘NHSvaccine’, include a link to the @NHSuk website, have the option to call 119, and will NOT ask for payment details https://t.co/GiotRtFsqm https://t.co/GSSbbcpQfM
